Reference Sources
=================

   Details on each file format were obtained from:

PlusD
     The documentation supplied with James Gasson's `Spectre' emulator
     for the Sam Coup'e. `Spectre' is available from









     `ftp://ftp.gns.getronics.nl/pub/os/sinclair/emulators/samcoupe/SPECTRE.zip'.

sna
     The `comp.sys.sinclair'/ZX Spectrum FAQ, available from
     `http://www.kendalls.demon.co.uk/cssfaq/index.html'.

snp
     The documentation supplied with Radovan Garabik's Nuclear ZX,
     which is available from










     `ftp://ftp.gns.getronics.nl/pub/os/sinclair/emulators/pc/dos/nuclear_zx.zip'.

sp
     The `comp.sys.sinclair'/ZX Spectrum FAQ, available from
