z80
     The documentation supplied with Gerton Lunter's `z80'. Version 3.05
     of `z80' is available from







     `ftp://ftp.gns.getronics.nl/pub/os/sinclair/emulators/pc/dos/z80-305.zip'.

zxs
     The `zx32' home page: `http://zx32.home.ml.org/' (the same
     information is in `zx32''s help file, under "Technical
     Information").

   There is a vast amount of information on the Spectrum, emulators and
the like available in the `comp.sys.sinclair' FAQ (see the sna entry
